item.title: 508 HD client and webclient
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

“error_game_js5io” means that the server you are attempting to connect to is offline. Change the IP or make sure the server you are connecting to is online before you run the client.

Furthermore, you are not giving 5 USD to anyone.
